#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Window Decoration Configuration Module</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Akna dekoratsioonide seadistamise moodul</screeninfo>"

